name: Morning in the Jungle: ArtbyGülsen x Eralore

metadata.name: Morning in the Jungle: ArtbyGülsen x Eralore
metadata.description:
"I promised Bahia we would go on an adventure today, gathering fruit and nuts from the trees. It will be good for us ladies to have some time alone." Elena, By Way of the Sea

As a full-time artist, Gülsen creates hand-drawn digital character and concept art. She believes in the magic of colors and likes to present that in her art. Her characters often reflect her feelings and sometimes the traces of the universe.
